          <source>This is shown in the following example, which has code that queries for whether it has the ability to save a file to the local disk:</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="218" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>If an application does not have the desired permission, the call to                          <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Security.CodeAccessPermission.Demand%2A&gt;</ph> will throw a security exception.</source>
        </trans-unit>
        <trans-unit id="219" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>Otherwise, the permission has been granted.</source>
        </trans-unit>
